 * [Hyperloop—a theoretical, 760 mph transit system made of sun, air, and magnets](http://arstechnica.com/business/2013/08/hyperloop-a-theoretical-760-mph-transit-system-made-of-sun-air-and-magnets) -- Ars Technica, 2013-08-13
